  m_text: '          In the mysterious land of Eldoria, an ancient foe has been awakened
    from a slumber lasting over a millennium. Known as the "Great Evil Rah''gorath",
    this entity has caused chaos and threatens the peace of the world. As a brave
    hero, you have been tasked with the mission to defeat Rah''gorath and restore
    peace to the land.'
